<HEADLINE> Marlins OF Bautista Hit in Head </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BOSTON (AP) -- Florida Marlins left fielder Danny Bautista left  
Sunday's game against the Boston Red Sox after a Pedro Martinez 
pitch hit him behind the left ear. 
</P>
